sequenceDiagram
    participant App as SpringApplication
    participant Selector as AutoConfigurationImportSelector
    participant Loader as SpringFactoriesLoader
    participant Meta as META-INF/spring.factories
    participant Cond as ConditionEvaluator
    participant Ctx as ApplicationContext

    App->>Selector: selectImports(AnnotationMetadata)
    Selector->>Loader: loadFactoryNames(EnableAutoConfiguration)
    Loader->>Meta: 读取所有 jar 中的 spring.factories
    Meta-->>Loader: 返回所有 AutoConfiguration 类名
    Loader-->>Selector: List<String>

    loop 每个候选 AutoConfiguration
        Selector->>Cond: shouldSkip(metadata)
        Cond-->>Selector: @ConditionalOnClass<br/>@ConditionalOnMissingBean<br/>@ConditionalOnProperty
    end

    Selector-->>App: 通过条件的 Configuration 类名数组
    App->>Ctx: 注册并实例化 Configuration
    Note over App,Ctx: 最终只装配符合条件的自动配置类
